SteamSale
  Ruby script for gathering sale infomation on Steam Store.

/* REQUIREMENT */
  ruby v1.8.7~
  rubygem
  hpricot - gem install hpricot

/* USAGE */

    $ruby main.rb (<url_list_file>)

  If url list file is omitted, load url.txt.
  Output is like 

   <a href="http://store.steampowered.com/***/" target="_blank">Game Title</a> $x.xx -> $y.yy (zz%off) 

/* SUPPORT */
